# The API reference is GENERATED from each package's XML docs at build time and
# never committed (Phase 8.4 design, decision 3; widened by #173). The `///` next to
# the code is the one home for those facts; a committed copy here would be a second
# one, and a second copy is the thing this whole site is built to refuse.
#   · Components -> docs/components/reference/   (historical home)
#   · every other generated package -> docs/reference/<package>/  (Device today)
docs/components/reference/
docs/reference/
